{"tid":301590,"cid":17,"subCid":0,"title":"[人體實驗][零準備]唔食得辣反kpop男子毒遊泡菜國十日","createTime":"2017-06-28T18:16:32.000Z","updateTime":"2017-06-29T04:05:11.000Z","uid":89595,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"e3d5088241b8037ca7a20742ddba2da028fadcdb","tid":301590,"uid":89595,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-28T18:16:32.000Z","msg":"。引子<br />\n三月嘅時候睇咗拜恩斯絲打嘅1500蚊七日挑戰post(由佢出完台灣post就深潛，情況令人擔憂<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> )<br />\n<br />\n咁啱嗰陣新識咗個朋友喺首爾讀書<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n講講下就趁UO 78蚊買咗飛仁川，<br />\n但因為搶遲咗嘅關係，<br />\n一係淨係去四日，一係去十日(晚機到早機走所以即係自動減兩日<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> )<br />\n就心諗反正呢個國家我呢世都唔會再嚟(好似係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> )<br />\n所以就把心一橫，買咗10日<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n雖然係10日咁長，<br />\n但其實我本身又唔中意泡菜，更加唔食得辣，<br />\n更甚嘅係我係No.1反kpop fans<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  <br />\n加上我係正常嘅雄性人類，既唔好濕平更唔會整容<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n所以想計下自己會用幾多錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我冇拜絲啲budget咁limited <br />\n但我都希望自己唔過2500<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n留返啲錢下年返我第二個家鄉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n呢個唔太算係直播遊記post（唔想用太多電話）<br />\n但我都希望盡量即時上報洗費<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n即使唔係每晚都一定會做個統計<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n希望可以控制到自己洗費<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n有閒都可以分享下見聞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n第一次出呢類post請多多指教<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0749a70008f7eb355bbabd83fa434e6a3a0a9407","tid":301590,"uid":89595,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-28T18:21:37.000Z","msg":"嚇撚死出咗post喺app唔見心諗唔係連連登都玩我啊嘛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7f5444e79f163843a1eec9ba19150fb48da47103","tid":301590,"uid":89595,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-28T18:30:17.000Z","msg":"係咪冇人睇到呢個post<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我重裝咗一次個app都唔見<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"891114aa95b3b038a0c517f2689b207cb6fb80a8","tid":301590,"uid":120581,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-28T18:31:38.000Z","msg":"辣殺"},{"pid":"eff97b6228f2b478ea9e9aafaa8950f3aa1f5b84","tid":301590,"uid":89595,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-28T18:49:20.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>辣殺</blockquote><br />\n巴打你係咪用web版<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ed2b7d27a4bc52978227940e26a9f0472d4d03cd","tid":301590,"uid":120581,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-28T19:06:45.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>辣殺</blockquote><br />\n巴打你係咪用web版<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n手機<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/09.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"87c6b64e524479ae26552abc8e4657cada259697","tid":301590,"uid":35746,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-28T23:25:38.000Z","msg":"留名"},{"pid":"f8544f470046a607b97ea35642a75f5d22c307bc","tid":301590,"uid":41112,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-29T02:41:24.000Z","msg":"無圖無人理咖"},{"pid":"4be24af145401f1cf904f201b47314c79822d13f","tid":301590,"uid":44318,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-29T02:44:12.000Z","msg":"lm"},{"pid":"3ad794c3f2c96a9d48def2f8ddf89b0f81cb1913","tid":301590,"uid":36157,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-29T03:54:43.